If you&rsquo;re working on the design of a website or web page, keep in mind that the beauty of visual style is not the deciding factor for success.
In fact, Vitaly Friedman, co-creator of the smashing magazine, said that &ldquo;usability and the utility, not the visual design, determine the success or failure of a web-site.&rdquo;
Unfortunately, designers tend to conceive trendy looking interfaces, without considering the user&rsquo;s needs. This is a problem, because it leads to a quantity of complex and inappropriate user intefaces.
